{"tid":1707683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角即時討論","createTime":"2019-11-11T11:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T12:38:38.000Z","uid":107681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4223e29d4f59d3b2909b052df3e4b15c5b00f74a","tid":1707683,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b069a99d262204cf9b058b4d2feb536cf50cf9","tid":1707683,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"又陣地?rb完仲唔散?"},{"pid":"d36102b91736fe6fd3ae9197d9c629082062d22f","tid":1707683,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:04:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11 12 朝早要人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n怕危險去搭鐵，一齊唔好落車大背囊，塞爆佢<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足rb 多用火魔鐵釘，拮爆車軚做rb<br />\n<br />\n流水式block ，彩虹戰衣加黑外套，不要停留太耐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又冇工會，好難逼人罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但如果主要道路死曬，公司都冇辦法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以要流水式block , block 完就走，去其他地方block , lunch time 會有打工仔接力遊行，block 到10點就ok 可以休息下"},{"pid":"b7b4ba3e1a0e64bebb847c8cb6654a4c0fe4e556","tid":1707683,"uid":7359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:09:18.000Z","msg":"旺角手足注意<br />\n油麻地站岩岩停咗<br />\n狗退去尖沙咀一半係食飯補充體力<br />\n另一半係block 曬啲巴士唔比佢地行<br />\n原本尖沙咀至油麻地段係有巴士<br />\n班狗厭阻住佢地<br />\n當中間啲車走曬班狗就會開始布袋陣包抄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打到呢到時收到電台講巴士公司要求所有司機離開"},{"pid":"d40b8b4bde7ce281a92b5d8235369179b1cb98f9","tid":1707683,"uid":147047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"聽到直升機聲"},{"pid":"6fa6b090ac5ed45d1e716a63fbebe7d2f65589bb","tid":1707683,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"閂左o既舖今日唔會再開得返架喇, 安全撒離緊要"},{"pid":"7d75903172d4a4bd9d317eab206b850d36d999f7","tid":1707683,"uid":65